<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>τῇ ἀδελφῇ Ἑρμείας χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>λοιπὸν τί σοι γράψω οὐκ<g type="apostrophe"/> οἶδα, <subst><add place="inline"><choice><corr>ἀπέκα-

    <lb n="3"/>μον</corr><sic>απαικακαμον</sic></choice></add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">απεκακαμον</del></subst> γάρ σοι <choice><corr>ἕκαστον</corr><sic>αικαστον</sic></choice> λέγων καὶ 

    <lb n="4"/>οὐκ<g type="apostrophe"/> <choice><corr>ἐνακούεις</corr><sic>αινακουεις</sic></choice>. χρὴ γάρ τινα ὁρῶν-

    <lb n="5"/>τα <choice><corr>ἑαυτὸν</corr><sic>αιαυτον</sic></choice> ἐν δυστυχίᾳ <choice><corr>καὶ ἂν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἀνα-

    <lb n="6"/>χωρεῖν</corr><sic>αναχωριν</sic></choice> καὶ μὴ ἁπλῶς <choice><corr>μάχεσθαι</corr><sic>μαχαισθαι</sic></choice> τῷ 

    <lb n="7"/>δεδογ<g type="apostrophe"/>μένῳ. μετρίων γὰρ καὶ δυσ-

    <lb n="8"/>τυχῶν γένεσιν <choice><corr>ἔχοντες</corr><sic>αιχοντες</sic></choice> οὐδὲ 

    <lb n="9"/>οὕτω <choice><corr>ἑαυτοῖς</corr><sic>αιαυτοις</sic></choice> <choice><corr>προσέχομεν</corr><sic>προσαιχομεν</sic></choice>. τέως 

    <lb n="10"/>μὲν οὖν οὐδὲν οὐδέπω <choice><corr>πέπρακται</corr><sic>παιπρακται</sic></choice>, 

    <lb n="11"/><choice><corr>καὶ ἂν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.316">ὡς, εἴπερ</lem><rdg>ὡσείπερ</rdg></app> <choice><corr>μέλει</corr><sic>μελι</sic></choice> σοι <choice><corr>ἀποστεῖλόν</corr><sic>αποστιλον</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="12"/>μοί τινα ἢ Γοῦ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>θον ἢ Ἀμμώνιον 

    <lb n="13"/>παραμένοντα μοι ἄχρις ἂν γνῶ 

    <lb n="14"/>πῶς τὰ κατ᾽ <choice><corr>ἐμὲ</corr><sic>αιμαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἀποτίθεται</corr><sic>αποτιθαιται</sic></choice>. μὴ ἆρα 

    <lb n="15"/>παρέλκομαι ἢ καὶ εἴργομαι ἔστ᾽ ἂν 

    <lb n="16"/>ὁ θεὸς ἡμᾶς <choice><corr>ἐλεήσῃ</corr><sic>αιλαιηση</sic></choice>; καὶ γὰρ Ἑ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρ</unclear>μ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">εία</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> 

    <lb n="17"/><choice><corr>ἐπείγεται</corr><sic>αιπειγεται</sic></choice> ἐλθεῖν πρὸς <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μᾶς, ἀλλὰ αὐ-

    <lb n="18"/>τὸν ἀξιώσας <choice><corr>παραμεῖναι</corr><sic>παραμιναι</sic></choice> οὐκ<g type="apostrophe"/> <choice><corr>ἐβου-

    <lb n="19"/>λήθη</corr><sic>αιβουληθη</sic></choice>, λέγων ὅτι ἀναγ<g type="apostrophe"/>καῖόν τι <choice><corr>ἔχω</corr><sic>αιχω</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="20"/>καὶ <choice><corr>δεῖ</corr><sic>δι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>με</corr><sic>μαι</sic></choice> ἀνελθεῖν, καὶ <hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi><hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>ὸς δὲ Γεννά-

    <lb n="21"/>διος οὐκ<g type="apostrophe"/> <choice><corr>οἷός</corr><sic><hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>ος</sic></choice> τέ ἐστιν <choice><corr>προσεδρεύειν</corr><sic>προσαιδρευει<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear></sic></choice> 

    <lb n="22"/><choice><corr>κτήσει</corr><sic>κτησι</sic></choice>, μάλιστα <choice><corr>ἐπὶ</corr><sic>επει</sic></choice> ξένης καὶ 

    <lb n="23"/>παρὰ τῇ <choice><corr>τάξει</corr><sic>ταξι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ὤν</corr><sic>οντα</sic></choice>. τὰ κατὰ σὲ διοίκη-

    <lb n="24"/>σον ὡς πρέπον ἐστίν, μὴ <choice><corr>τέλειον</corr><sic>τελεον</sic></choice> ἀνα-

    <lb n="25"/>τραπῶμεν. οὐ δέδοκται γὰρ ἡμῖν <choice><corr>ἔχειν</corr><sic>αιχιν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="26"/>τι δυστυχοῦντες. ἔ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρ</supplied>ρωσό μοι διὰ παντὸς 

    <lb n="27"/>εὖ πράσ<g type="apostrophe"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied>ουσα. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἑρμείας Γού<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>θῳ <hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi><hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>ῷ <expan>χα<ex cert="high">ίρειν</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="2"/>εἰ μὴ Ἀμμώνιος πάραυτα 

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>ἔρχεται</corr><sic>ερχαιται</sic></choice> πρός <choice><corr>με</corr><sic>μαι</sic></choice>, σὺ αὐτὸς 

    <lb n="4"/>πάντα <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>περθέμενος 

    <lb n="5"/>ἢ καὶ <choice><corr>ἐκείνου</corr><sic>αικεινου</sic></choice> τὸ σὸν ἔργον 

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr>ποιοῦντος</corr><sic>ποιουντα</sic></choice>. <choice><corr>ἀλ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">λ</supplied>᾽</corr><sic>αλ<g type="apostrophe"/></sic></choice> ὅρα μὴ <choice><corr>κα-

    <lb n="7"/>ταλείψῃς</corr><sic>καταλιψῃς</sic></choice> <choice><corr>με</corr><sic>μαι</sic></choice> θλιβόμενον. 

    <lb n="8"/>καὶ δήλωσόν μοι πῶς ἔσ-

    <lb n="9"/>χεν Δίδυμος· μὴ ἆρα αἱ ἡ-

    <lb n="10"/>μέραι τὰ πάντα διατελοῦσι; 

    <lb n="11"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε <expan>εὔχο<ex cert="high">μαι</ex></expan>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.31346" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.31346" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="201" notAfter="300">III</date></p></div><div n="meta.31346" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BL VII, S. 127.</p></div><div n="meta.31346" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.31346" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">120</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">31346</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">120</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;1;120" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.31346" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.31346" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Sel. Pap. I 162</bibl><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Naldini, Cristianesimo 62</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.31346" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de" default="NO"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Schubart, Ein Jahrtausend am Nil (1912) 87 und (1923) 89.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="en" default="NO"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Winter, Life and Letters (1933), S. 105</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.31346" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>